data.description: Welcome to this charming raised-ranch home nestled on a spacious .41-acre lot. With 4 bedrooms this home caters to your various needs whether it’s extra space for a home office or an extra guest room. The ¾ bath is conveniently located off the back door to facilitate clean up from yard duty. The lower level has an additional living area with a propane stove for keeping you warm on those cooler evenings while enjoying a good movie. The double-car detached garage sits conveniently adjacent to the main house, offering ample space for parking and a workshop area, catering to those with hobbies or projects in mind. Beyond the walls of the home, the .41-acre lot provides an outdoor oasis. The yard is an excellent canvas for gardening, barbecues, gatherings or recreational activities making it perfect for creating lasting memories. New roof and floor coverings installed in 2022. Call and make your appointment today!
